data.description: Beautifully maintained & updated with split floor plan! Vaulted foyer ceilings & fresh neutral paint accompany the formal living and dining room combination. Move into the updated kitchen & breakfast area with the must have items - exquisite cabinetry, granite countertops, island, raised breakfast bar, gas cooktop & added bonus of pantry plus a separate walk in pantry laundry room combination. The open concept floor plan allows you to gaze past the breakfast bar into the generously sized living room complete with fireplace. Down the hallway awaits a powder bath & 5th bedroom or office with lovely french doors, & huge under the stair closet. Upstairs you are welcomed by the 3rd living space. The primary suite is completely separate from 3 generously sized bedrooms and features private ensuite with dual vanities, separate shower, garden tub, built ins & walk in closet. Complete downstairs 3 ton gas system replaced 2023. New water heater Feb. 2024. MISD & quick highway access. This is it!
